---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Atupri - Simplifying Insurance Decisions"
  description="Redesigning a premium calculator and product comparison tool to make insurance options transparent and easier to compare for customers."
>
  <!-- Hero - Full Width -->
  <section class="relative">
    <!-- Back button -->
    <div class="px-6 md:px-20 py-8">
      <a href="/#work" class="inline-flex items-center text-body text-text-secondary hover:text-accent transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        Back to Work
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Content -->
    <div class="px-6 md:px-20 pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-accent/10 text-accent rounded-full text-body-sm font-medium">UX/UI Design</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-secondary text-text-secondary rounded-full text-body-sm">2022</span>
          <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-secondary text-text-secondary rounded-full text-body-sm">Atupri</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-h1-mobile md:text-h1 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-6 leading-tight">
          Simplifying Insurance Decisions
        </h1>

        <p class="text-body-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          Redesigning a premium calculator and product comparison tool to make insurance options transparent and easier to compare for customers.
        </p>

        <!-- Tags -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-8">
          <span class="text-caption text-text-secondary bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-border">product comparison</span>
          <span class="text-caption text-text-secondary bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-border">design system</span>
          <span class="text-caption text-text-secondary bg-white px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-border">mobile-first</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Image - Full Width -->
    <div class="w-full">
      <img
        src="/images/projects/atupri/Home.png"
        alt="Atupri Premium Calculator"
        class="w-full h-auto"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <article>
    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32 bg-secondary/30">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">The Challenge</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Atupri's product portfolio was complex and difficult for customers to navigate, resulting in low clarity when comparing insurance options. A new supplementary product needed to be integrated seamlessly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">My Role</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Concept design, interface design, visual design, usability testing
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">The Solution</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              A streamlined interface leveraging existing components to showcase Atupri's product offerings in a clear, intuitive way - making insurance comparison quick and effortless.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Problem Section -->
    <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">The Problem</h2>

        <p class="text-body-lg text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Choosing health insurance is already stressful. When the interface is confusing and products are hard to compare, it becomes overwhelming.
        </p>

        <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Atupri had a new supplementary insurance product to launch, but their existing premium calculator made it difficult for customers to understand and compare options. The complex product portfolio created friction in the decision-making process.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/5 to-purple-50 border-l-4 border-accent px-8 py-6 rounded-r-xl mb-8">
          <p class="text-body-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">
            How might we simplify insurance comparison to help customers make confident decisions quickly?
          </p>
        </div>

        <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          The client requested that we utilize existing design components where possible while creating a more cohesive, transparent experience that would drive sales for both new and existing products.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Section -->
    <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32 bg-secondary/30">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">The Process</h2>

        <p class="text-body-lg text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-12">
          We completed the project in 5 weeks, moving from discovery to handover with a structured, collaborative approach.
        </p>

        <div class="mb-12">
          <img
            src="/images/projects/atupri/Process.png"
            alt="Atupri Project Process Timeline"
            class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-medium"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Week 1: Kick-off Workshop</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Aligned with stakeholders on project goals, scope, and expectations. Tapped into team knowledge about user needs and business constraints.
            </p>
            <img
              src="/images/projects/atupri/Kick-off.png"
              alt="Kick-off Workshop"
              class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-soft"
            />
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Week 2: Competitor Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Analyzed competitor insurance calculators to identify strengths, weaknesses, and opportunities for differentiation. This informed our design direction and feature priorities.
            </p>
            <a href="/images/projects/atupri/Competitor analysis.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block group cursor-zoom-in">
              <img
                src="/images/projects/atupri/Competitor analysis.png"
                alt="Competitor Analysis"
                class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-soft transition-all duration-300 group-hover:shadow-medium group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
              />
              <p class="text-caption text-text-tertiary text-center mt-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Click to enlarge</p>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Week 3: Design Exploration</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Explored multiple interface concepts, focusing on clarity and ease of comparison. Worked closely with a UX writer to refine language and terminology.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Week 4: Prototyping & Testing</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
              Created web and mobile prototypes, then conducted usability testing. The tests validated our design while highlighting areas for refinement in UX writing and visual hierarchy.
            </p>
            <a href="/images/projects/atupri/Usability testing.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block group cursor-zoom-in">
              <img
                src="/images/projects/atupri/Usability testing.png"
                alt="Usability Testing Results"
                class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-soft transition-all duration-300 group-hover:shadow-medium group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
              />
              <p class="text-caption text-text-tertiary text-center mt-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Click to enlarge</p>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Week 5: Specifications & Handover</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Documented design specifications and handed off to the development team with clear guidelines for implementation.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Solution Section -->
    <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">The Solution</h2>

        <p class="text-body-lg text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-12">
          We created a streamlined premium calculator that makes comparing insurance products quick and effortless, increasing transparency and customer confidence.
        </p>

        <a href="/images/projects/atupri/Final design.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block group cursor-zoom-in mb-16">
          <img
            src="/images/projects/atupri/Final design.png"
            alt="Atupri Final Design"
            class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-medium transition-all duration-300 group-hover:shadow-large group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
          />
          <p class="text-caption text-text-tertiary text-center mt-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Click to enlarge</p>
        </a>

        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Clear Product Comparison</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Products are displayed side-by-side with clear visual hierarchy, making it easy to scan and compare coverage options, prices, and benefits at a glance.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Improved Language & Terminology</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Working closely with a UX writer, we refined insurance terminology to be clear, understandable, and easy to scan - removing jargon and reducing cognitive load.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Design System Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-6">
              We utilized Atupri's existing design system components while creating new ones where needed, maintaining consistency with their brand while pushing design boundaries.
            </p>
            <a href="/images/projects/atupri/Design system.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block group cursor-zoom-in">
              <img
                src="/images/projects/atupri/Design system.png"
                alt="Atupri Design System"
                class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-soft transition-all duration-300 group-hover:shadow-medium group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
              />
              <p class="text-caption text-text-tertiary text-center mt-4 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors duration-300">Click to enlarge</p>
            </a>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Mobile-First Approach</h3>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              By carefully analyzing user behavior and preferences, we ensured the mobile experience was intuitive and user-friendly - critical for customers comparing insurance on the go.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Impact Section -->
    <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-20 md:py-32 bg-secondary/30">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-h2-mobile md:text-h3 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Impact & Learnings</h2>

        <p class="text-body-lg text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-12">
          Usability testing validated that our streamlined interface allowed for quick and effortless comparison, promoting transparency and facilitating the purchasing process.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-3">Language Matters</h4>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Working closely with a UX writer was essential. Refining language and terminology made the premium calculator and product map clearer, more understandable, and easier to scan.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-3">Integration Requires Empathy</h4>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Integrating new products into an existing service portfolio requires careful consideration of how they fit into the overall user experience. We created a cohesive journey that promoted transparency and ease of use.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border">
            <h4 class="text-h4 font-serif font-bold text-text-primary mb-3">Consistency Through Components</h4>
            <p class="text-body text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              Utilizing existing components was an effective way to streamline the design process and maintain consistency - while still allowing room for innovation where needed.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>

  <!-- Back to Work CTA -->
  <section class="px-6 md:px-20 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <Button href="/#work" variant="secondary" size="large">
        ‚Üê Back to All Work
      </Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
